item.title: Wth is wrong with my cmd?
item.dc:creator: @jme jme
item.description:
@jme wrote:

You likely messed up your “path” and its not pointing to where tools like ipconfig are stored.

This happened to me in XP so i’m not sure the exact procedure for vista/win7. But in xp: go to your environmental variables and under system click PATH and edit it. Add in: %SystemRoot%\system32;%SystemRoot%;%SystemRoot%\System32\wbem
